  "relative_mass_audit": "WFR-FM experiment_runner.compute_relative_mass(df) computes per-timepoint sample-size ratios and passes them to pretrain(..., relative_mass=...). train.pretrain forwards this object to utils.get_batch as the argument named ratios, but utils.get_batch never reads ratios; compute_uot_plans also sets source and target masses a and b to ones. Therefore, in the audited source, compute_relative_mass does not affect training.",
